Kubara

Inzovu imwe yagiye kunywa amazi.

Udusumbashyamba tubiri tugiye kunywa amazi.

Hano hari inyana eshatu n'inyoni enye. Zose Zagiye kunywa amazi.

Impala eshanu hamwe ningurube esheshatu zo mu gasozi zigiye kunywa amazi.

Ibikeri birindwi n'amafi umunani biri mu mazi.

Imparage icyenda zigiye kunywa amazi.

Intare imwe yaje kunywa amazi.

Ninde ufite ubutwari bwo gukomeza kunywa?
